title: Capital One League Cup Show Highlights 720p 29.10.2014 BBC
description:
Capital One League Cup Show Highlights 4th round 29.10.2014 

Duration: 1 hour 

Manish Bhasin presents action from the League Cup. 
With sixteen teams remaining, the tournament reaches the fourth round. 
There are highlights from the Etihad as cup holders Manchester City meet Newcastle United. 
Meanwhile, Tottenham entertain Brighton and West Bromwich Albion take a trip to Bournemouth.
